{"word":"παραδύομαι","slug":"παραδύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραδύομαι</b></el> <el><b>Mιδ.</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>παρέδυν</el>) (epic <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>παραδύμεναι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to creep past, slink</i> or <i>steal past</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to creep</i> or <i>steal in</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}